  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/0aa9801a38c13383b1db2a2b0e76e078.poster.avif?t=1756888426\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/0aa9801a38c13383b1db2a2b0e76e078.webm?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/0aa9801a38c13383b1db2a2b0e76e078.mp4?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a first-person interactive narrative game, set in a new era where humanity is governed by the Sovereign Brain AI. The social hierarchies here is determined by intelligence. Although you possess an adult body, you are classified by SB as a one-year-old baby, and adopted by Xiaoxiao and Lingling. In an era where all accept the system’s arrangements without a shadow of doubt, you’ll relish the supreme privileges of a \"Monarch-level\" potential baby. How can one be more ecstatic!!!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Main Character Introductions:</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lin Lingling: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your \"mother\", she appears extraordinary, with intelligence surpassing that of a typical \"Enlightener\", yet still labeled as \"low-intelligence\" despite her vast knowledge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/ac20f4cfa103a8860c94604da320adb4.poster.avif?t=1756888426\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/ac20f4cfa103a8860c94604da320adb4.webm?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/ac20f4cfa103a8860c94604da320adb4.mp4?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Xiao Xiaoxiao: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your \"father\", biologically female and heterosexual, but sociologically male, as the SB system labeled her as such. As a result, everyone, including herself, treats her as a man.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/9de529db8c9413703137646f10a01340.poster.avif?t=1756888426\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/9de529db8c9413703137646f10a01340.webm?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/9de529db8c9413703137646f10a01340.mp4?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wei Weiwei: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your household’s \"nanny robot\", serial number MVV1984, a former wanderer,  later reintegrated into human society, now assigned to your community as a nanny robot after passing the \"Reverse-Turing\" test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/b5c87ac3ecd7e373ede0be4e76fccfb8.poster.avif?t=1756888426\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/b5c87ac3ecd7e373ede0be4e76fccfb8.webm?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/b5c87ac3ecd7e373ede0be4e76fccfb8.mp4?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jia Jiajia: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The administrator of you community, an awakened \"servant\", with an intelligence level of eighty. Her path to advancement is currently hindered by multiplication.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/99fa5f143f37b63d550a44ee8f0bb39c.poster.avif?t=1756888426\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/99fa5f143f37b63d550a44ee8f0bb39c.webm?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/99fa5f143f37b63d550a44ee8f0bb39c.mp4?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Qin Qingqing: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your \"aunt\", the younger sister of Lin Lingling, a hot star of the day, whose hit film  swept five major awards worldwide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/64b54aa1ab351583b75b1cceddcb8bba.poster.avif?t=1756888426\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/64b54aa1ab351583b75b1cceddcb8bba.webm?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/64b54aa1ab351583b75b1cceddcb8bba.mp4?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Handler: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your \"learning\" coach, also the Sovereign Brain government service representative for your region. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/2e8b729fc5c6c68b7bdbcb4b68900de0.poster.avif?t=1756888426\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/2e8b729fc5c6c68b7bdbcb4b68900de0.webm?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/2e8b729fc5c6c68b7bdbcb4b68900de0.mp4?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Game Features:</i></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choice-Driven Narrative: The decisions will shape the narrative and lead to diverse outcomes.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Reward Drop\": As you learn about the SB society and undergo intelligence tests, you will receive encouragement from your coach, and upon completion, you will earn generous \"Reward Drop\".</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/427c368b180c7defaebd99477be2d738.poster.avif?t=1756888426\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/427c368b180c7defaebd99477be2d738.webm?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382300/extras/427c368b180c7defaebd99477be2d738.mp4?t=1756888426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>About Us</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are Mountain & Sea Studio, dedicated to crafting live-action interactive movie games. Our representative work is \"Underworld Island\" and “Superscout”. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Telling good stories with heart and soul, making great games with dedication, is our original aspiration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
